DraftCode Privacy Policy
DraftCode operates locally on your iOS device only. There are no servers or cloud service required to use it.
No personal data is collected by Solesignal Ltd. Any collection of analytics related to the App Store or regarding Crash Reports is performed by Apple and governed by Apple’s privacy policy.
If you email Solesignal Ltd. for technical support, your email address and any information you volunteer will be used for the sole purpose of providing technical support, and may be retained for reference in future support requests. Email addresses obtained from support requests are not sold nor subscribed to marketing or promotional lists of any kind.
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
If you have any questions regarding this policy, please do not hesitate to contact us.
